---
// The Observatory Contact — Minimalista centrado, puro
---

<section id="contacto" class="py-20 md:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 text-center">
    
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="font-mono text-xs text-dmk-accent uppercase tracking-widest">04 / Contacto</div>
      
      <h2 class="font-mono text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-dmk-text uppercase tracking-tight">
        INICIAR
      </h2>
      
      <p class="font-mono text-sm text-dmk-muted leading-relaxed">
        Todo proyecto comienza con un diagnóstico de datos. No vendemos presentaciones; co-diseñamos soluciones medibles.
      </p>
    </div>

    <form class="mt-16 space-y-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Nombre" class="bg-transparent border-b border-dmk-muted/30 text-dmk-text font-mono text-sm py-3 focus:outline-none focus:border-dmk-accent transition-colors placeholder:text-dmk-muted/50"/>
        <input type="email" placeholder="Email" class="bg-transparent border-b border-dmk-muted/30 text-dmk-text font-mono text-sm py-3 focus:outline-none focus:border-dmk-accent transition-colors placeholder:text-dmk-muted/50"/>
      </div>
      <input type="text" placeholder="Cargo / Empresa" class="w-full bg-transparent border-b border-dmk-muted/30 text-dmk-text font-mono text-sm py-3 focus:outline-none focus:border-dmk-accent transition-colors placeholder:text-dmk-muted/50"/>
      <textarea placeholder="Describe tu desafío..." rows="4" class="w-full bg-transparent border-b border-dmk-muted/30 text-dmk-text font-mono text-sm py-3 focus:outline-none focus:border-dmk-accent transition-colors resize-none placeholder:text-dmk-muted/50"></textarea>
      
      <button type="submit" class="mt-8 px-8 py-3 bg-dmk-accent text-dmk-bg font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider font-bold hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
        Enviar →
      </button>
    </form>

    <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-dmk-muted/10 space-y-2 font-mono text-xs text-dmk-muted">
      <p>Santiago, Chile</p>
      <p>contacto@datametrik.cl</p>
      <p>+56 2 2244 8800</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
